333
00:24:30,580 --> 00:24:35,050
[The enchanted sword known as the "Star Destroyer"! Will the secret of the wooden sword be revealed?!]

334
00:24:35,510 --> 00:24:37,550
Hey, Shimura. Behind you.

335
00:24:37,550 --> 00:24:39,010
Huh? Oh...

